Variables are set using the Cset command. See 'Info Cset' for an
explanation of its use.

The following variables are available for use by Clerics:

Variable		Usage
=======================	=====================================
pie			The default pie type used for the
			gpie and fpie emotes.
loginmsg		The message seen by all the guild
			upon the Cleric's login.  *
logoutmsg		The message seen by all the guild
			upon the Cleric's logout. *
hammerspam		Set to a number from 0 to 100 to
			control how often your hammer will
			spam. If set to 100, it will spam
			all the time. The damage that your
			hammer does will remain the same
			whether you hammer spams or not.

* NOTE: There are no filters in place for these but if I see
	them used inappropriately, sanctions and or filters
	will be forthcoming.

